不管什么原因</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">我没能参加这一期的加油</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">!2008.</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">首先最让我觉得对不起的是星星</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">我让他对我的期待落了空</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">想起我们在游乐场玩乐时他快乐的表情</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">我非常非常的想他</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">也想致以深深</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">深深地歉意</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.前</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">晚终于和他联系上了</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">听到他有些失落的声音</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">心里更歉疚</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">希望今后的时光</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">能给他更多的关心</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">唯一开心的是</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">他很希望送去的</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&lt;</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">灌篮高手</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&gt;.</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">还有我最爱的</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&lt;</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">蜡笔小新</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&gt;,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">早订好了全套</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">可惜这次没能亲手交给他</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">希望他回到学校里</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">这些书能带给他更多的快乐</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.....</SPAN></P>
