-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">是一种荣誉</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">第一次参加时</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">去学了艺术体操</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">,</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">不会忘记彩排那天导演及所有工作人员在旁边给予我的鼓励及支持</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">是他们的爱心促成了这次大型的公益筹款活动</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">希望今后有机会弥补这次的遗憾</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">.</SPAN></P>
