i; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">古人语</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">:"</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">滴水恩当涌泉报</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">",</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin">我一直心存感激</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">...</SPAN></P>
